          "reviewBody": "The school is so best. It has many facility like Computer Lab\nScience Labs\nMath's Lab\nIndoor games\nLandscaped Area\nSpacious library\nPrayer/Meditation Hall.\nMusic Room\nCanteen\nTransport Facility\nDance Room\nActivity room\nAuditorium\nKarate/ Yoga\nSwimming Pool and so all.",
